Welcome to the VOCP voice messaging system.

For the latest version and complete documentation, see the official website at:
http://www.VOCPsystem.com

Also BE SURE to have a look in the doc/ directory.

The VOCP system is a complete voice messaging solution, featuring voicemail boxes, email pagers and DTMF command shells.  Users can navigate the system using a touch-tone phone, leave and retrieve messages and execute programs on the host machine using the DTMF command shells.

VOCP now features a graphical configuration utility, a message retrieval, call center and faxing GUIs, as well as the core VOCP voice messaging system and the VOCPweb web interface.  


We are interested in knowing how you are using VOCP!  Drop us a line on the http://www.psychogenic.com contact page and let us know what you think!

