Address bug reports and comments to: prog AT vocpsystem.com or through the contact page on http://www.psychogenic.com

When sending bug reports, please provide the version of VOCP, the version of Perl, the version of your mgetty/vgetty, and the name and version of the operating system you are using.  If the problem is even remotely modem dependent, please provide information about the affected modems as well. 


For complete installation instructions, see the INSTALL file.


